Package org.openscience.cdk.iupac.parser

The core classes of the ChemNomParse project, an open source attempt of a chemical nomenclature parser, call via generate (name).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NomParserConstants
    Token literal values and constants.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttachedGroup
    Holds data on a specific functional group or substituent.
    MoleculeBuilder
    Takes in parsed Tokens from NomParser and contains rules to convert those tokens to a Molecule.
    NomParser
    A class partly generated by JavaCC which breaks down the chemical name into computable subparts and passes these parts to the MoleculeBuilder.
    NomParserTokenManager
    Token Manager.
    SimpleCharStream
    An implementation of interface CharStream, where the stream is assumed to contain only ASCII characters (without unicode processing).
    Token
    Describes the input token stream.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParseException
    This exception is thrown when parse errors are encountered.
  • Error Summary 
    Error Description
    TokenMgrError
    Token Manager Error.

Package org.openscience.cdk.iupac.parser Description

The core classes of the ChemNomParse project, an open source attempt of a chemical nomenclature parser, call via generate (name). See ChemNomParse Project Page for more information.
